### Quick start

```shell
# Add LesliBell engine
bundle add lesli_bell
```

```shell
# Setup database
rake lesli:db:setup
```

```ruby
# Load LesliBell
Rails.application.routes.draw do
    mount LesliBell::Engine => "/bell"
end
```
